'''Institute of Forest Biodiversity (IFB)'''<ref>http://ifb.icfre.gov.in/</ref> is a Research institute situated in [[Hyderabad]] in state of [[Telangana]]. It works under the [[Indian Council of Forestry Research and Education]] (ICFRE)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.icfre.org// |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-08-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20020811000115/http://www.icfre.org/ |archivedate=2002-08-11 |df= }}</ref> of the [[Ministry of Environment, Forests and Climate Change(India)|Ministry of Environment, Forests and Climate Change]], [[Government of India|Govt. of India]].<ref>http://www.envfor.nic.in/</ref>
